            "body": "Swedish etiquette grows out of a deep belief in egalitarianism and mutual respect. A key concept is 'Lagom'—the pursuit of moderation and balance, which translates into avoiding affectation or excessive expressiveness. The psychology of relationships here is based on trust and individual autonomy, alongside a strong sense of responsibility for the community. Understanding these mechanisms makes it possible to build lasting, authentic bonds based on partnership rather than hierarchy or material status.",
            "title": "Cultural Note"
